{"tid":946948,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏]捷克總理下令辦公室停用華為手機","createTime":"2018-12-19T01:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T02:16:08.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fd1b6fd83b5a9a0918ef2a562ded4f78021d4aec","tid":946948,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20181219/s00005/1545178377911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00005%2F1545178377911&d=MgGw1fxvt6eEJPHkMJ7ZStZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=53fd86fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00005%2F1545178377911&h=0c24c804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20181219/s00005/1545178377911</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克總理巴比什於當地時間周二（18日）下令，其政府辦公室禁止使用中國華為手機。捷克工業和貿易部表示會跟隨總理要求，而其他使用華為產品的政府部門可能會仿效。<br />\n<br />\n捷克國家網絡與信息安全局周一（17日）曾警告，華為和中興通訊製造的硬件和軟件構成安全威脅。華為否認指控。<br />\n<br />\n美國近月向其他國家施壓，要求限制使用華為的技術，因可能被監視及竊取信息。目前日本、澳洲及新西蘭等國響應。<br />\n<br />\n(美國廣播公司)"},{"pid":"f82738eedec8cc7756084f8de5d1a51754e0890e","tid":946948,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T02:16:08.000Z","msg":"中國最好的產品唔應該出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}